# üåç Global Nuclear Construction Tracker

A Streamlit app to track global nuclear energy construction activity and relevant news, categorized by country and reactor type.

## Features

- Interactive project explorer with country + reactor filters
- Live nuclear energy news scraped from World Nuclear News
- Clean, wide-layout dashboard UI

## Setup

```bash
git clone https://github.com/youruser/nuclear-tracker.git
cd nuclear-tracker
pip install -r requirements.txt
streamlit run streamlit_app.py
